title: Musictube 1.6 Multilingual + Patch [4REALTORRENTZ]
description:
Listen to millions of songs on YouTube in a convenient way, much like using a traditional player. Musictube plays album tracks in their original order and integrates album covers, artist pictures and lyrics.

Features:

Lots of music
Musictube can play full albums or even discographies of millions of artists present on YouTube.

Studio, live or cover?
Don't limit yourself to the original studio version. Listen to a live performance or to a surprising cover version.

Let the playlist rock
Musictube has a fully editable playlist you can fill in seconds and let play for hours.

Video, small and large
You can always show the video as a thumbnail or full-window. Handy for official music videos, live performances and covers.

Instructions:

1. Unpack and install
2. Close and copy patch to installation directory
3. Select which product you want to register and patch
4. Done
